message.body: I pet Frankie a bunch. She always tries to bite me after a couple of minutes or seconds
Me too. Don't feel too bad. I'm going to a pretty remote place for two days. A little nervous:/
Should be fun though. Saw a lot of art today. Then went to a noise show in a warehouse. Climbed a mountain. Ate huevos rancheros. Felt dehydrated all day. Water is hard to get.
You shoulda brought my water bottle. The cats have been sleeping together in my studio and leaving me to sleep all alone
I really should have brought it My fungus is growing up my arm. The cats are going to revolt.
